reviews.reviewText: Easy to hook up in car. Gets loose over time, but you just have to tighten the knob back up and it’s fine. Super cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was honestly shocked at how well this grips onto my Mini Coopers vents. Through all the bumps and whatnot this holder is super sturdy and didn't send my phone flying like my popsocket one used to lol.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price!
reviews.reviewText: This is super cute and such a good deal for the price! Was a little surprised it’s a weighted mechanism, it uses your phones weight to close around it so always double check your phone is secure before taking off! I have an iPhone pro max 12 and I noticed it will sometimes be a bit loose, but it’s easily fixed by gently pushing the phone down in the holder. Also has fallen out of my vents a few times but I don’t think that’s a design error more my vents in my Highlander aren’t the best for this type of holder as the slats are super close together. I get lots of compliments and have enjoyed having it as a fun addition to my car aesthetics

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars it’s so cute!!
reviews.reviewText: i was weary of getting this because it had no reviews, but i’m so glad i did! this mount is so cute! it’s easy to install and is very sturdy when driving (phone doesn’t move and mount stays in place). you just clip it to your vent and you’re good to go!! be aware that this DOES NOT CHARGE YOUR PHONE… it just holds it up while you drive (which is perfect for me). this buy was definitely worth it.

reviews.reviewText: This is great. Cute, and really amaze for the car. Had for 3 months, hasn’t fallen off or broken, and super easy to put back on if I needed to.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Not worth it for the price
reviews.reviewText: It's a cute phone mount, but I ended up returning it because the combined weight of it and my phone was too heavy for the car vents. It also didn't grip my phone, like, at all (my phone was more or less resting in it, not being held by it). I don't recommend this because it's heavy enough to move the vent whenever you make a turn - which is highly inconvenient since no one wants to readjust their phone mount all the time (kinda defeats the whole purpose of even having a phone mount)
